<emphasis bold="true" box="[757,855,1631,1657]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65">sp. nov.</emphasis>
</taxonomicNameLabel>
is named in memory of Charles Paul Alexander (
<number box="[414,546,1672,1698]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="1935.5" valueMax="1982.0" valueMin="1889.0">
<date box="[414,546,1672,1698]" pageId="4" pageNumber="65" value="1889" valueMax="1982">1889-1982</date>
</number>
